divs: Sighting DetailsI work night as a custodian and typicaly have to go out side to take out the trash. I alway take my camera every where I go inacase I see something neat. So anyways I was taken the trash out and noticed a blinking star in the sky pulled out my camera and took a picture. At the time i didnt know what it was and i still dont know exactly what it is but this is what i seen when i up loaded it after work.
